divs: Sighting DetailsWas taking pics of the smoke to compare the change each morning - just before sunrise. Caught this strange formation of 5 objects, hard to tell what they are - thought maybe helicopters ? but that would be odd because supposedly helicopters were unable to fly at the time due to strong winds (and if they are, why would they all be in one place, when there were so many fires burning in different places?).
Summary: Strange formation caught in pics during San Diego wildfires
